  <title>How to Schedule Automatic Updates?</title>

  <p>Update scheduling is used to perform automatic updates using <gui>KSO</gui> (<gui>KOOMPI System Operator</gui>) at fixed intervals, such as <gui>Weekly</gui> or <gui>Monthly</gui>.</p>
  
  <p>The default setting is "<gui>Weekly</gui>" to perform automatic updates at weekly intervals.</p>
  
